                    <span>This is very well laid-out, user-friendly book covering a huge range of topics. Start with this one, move on to some hands-on lessons, and then get the annapolis book of seamnship. From there, you should have quite a good knowledge base on which to build.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">I demand to immediately be taken to Bali! ;)</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>7</span>
